ing: 1 tablespoon finely chopped walnuts, or to taste
n: Raw Food Snacks - Cinnamon Bun Balls
des: "These lovely raw food snacks tastes just like cinnamon buns. They are simply delicious. Try them!"
ins: Blend 1/2 cup walnuts, dates, cinnamon, and cardamom together in a blender until almost smooth. Roll mixture into little balls. Place finely chopped walnuts in a shallow bowl and roll balls in walnuts to coat. Store balls in refrigerator.
